 1. City
Add City
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cities
Valid JSON Body:

{
  "cityName": "Gobi"
}

‚ùå Add City (Empty cityName)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cities
Invalid JSON Body:

{
  "cityName": ""
}
Expected Error: Error: City name is required.

Get All Cities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cities

Get City by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cities/1

